rows.label: qev015003_MSG0014
rows.name: No... NO! Get away from me![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0015
rows.name: Don't come any...closer... NO! STAY BACK![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_JNK0010
rows.name: Soothe

rows.label: qev015003_SEL0011
rows.name: Try to calm Phina down.

rows.label: qev015003_JNK0020
rows.name: Show Tough Love

rows.label: qev015003_SEL0021
rows.name: Yell at Phina until she snaps out of it.

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0016
rows.name: H-huh? Oh. R-right...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0017
rows.name: Gyaaah![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0018
rows.name: You... You're here for me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0019
rows.name: Oh, thank goodness...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0020
rows.name: But they... Grette is...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0021
rows.name: AAAAAAGH! Those monsters... They...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_JNK0030
rows.name: Question

rows.label: qev015003_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Phina what happened.

rows.label: qev015003_JNK0040
rows.name: Evacuate

rows.label: qev015003_SEL0041
rows.name: Flee with Phina from the cave.

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0022
rows.name: The Prone were going to eat me first... But Grette...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0023
rows.name:
She told them she'd be more tender than a flabby
human like me...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0024
rows.name: She knew she was provoking them, but she still...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_JNK0100
rows.name: Evacuate

rows.label: qev015003_SEL0101
rows.name: Flee with Phina from the cave.

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0025
rows.name:
The whole time we were in here, Grette kept saying it
was over.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0026
rows.name: That if Adelbert was gone, she had nothing to live for.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0027
rows.name:
So when they came for us, she offered to...die for me.
Said it was the last thing she could do for a friend.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0028
rows.name:
Right before they... She said to keep hope and live.
To live for the both of us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_JNK0060
rows.name: Probe

rows.label: qev015003_SEL0061
rows.name: Press Phina for more details.

rows.label: qev015003_JNK0080
rows.name: Evacuate

rows.label: qev015003_SEL0081
rows.name: Flee with Phina from the cave.

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0051
rows.name:
Grette took my place. The Prone dragged her into the
middle of the cave, and they...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0029
rows.name:
They started skinning her. ...Like meat.
They didn't realize she was a mimeosome,
and when they found out, they were furious.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0030
rows.name:
They...they tore her apart while I watched...
They pulled her piece from piece while she screamed
Adelbert's name.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0031
rows.name:
Those monsters made it last. She was half in pieces by
the time the screaming stopped, and then...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0032
rows.name: Oh, Grette... I can't... I...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0033
rows.name: Aah... AAAAAAAAAAAAAAUGH![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_JNK0070
rows.name: Soothe

rows.label: qev015003_SEL0071
rows.name: Try to calm Phina down.

rows.label: qev015003_JNK0090
rows.name: Evacuate

rows.label: qev015003_SEL0091
rows.name: Flee with Phina from the cave.

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0035
rows.name: R-right...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0036
rows.name: ...I'll make them pay. I swear it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0037
rows.name: No. Not until I've made them pay.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0038
rows.name:
You have to kill those Prone. Kill all of them.
That's what she kept me alive to do.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0039
rows.name:
They dragged her off. All of her...pieces.
Like they were going to use her for something.
I think they had some kind of orders to do that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0040
rows.name: Please. I can't just run away.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0041
rows.name:
I'm begging you, find those Prone—and their boss—
and give them what they gave Grette. End them.
End them ALL.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0042
rows.name:
The Prone were acting under orders from someone.
It's that abomination's fault that Grette and Adelbert
are dead.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0043
rows.name:
I'm begging you, find those Prone—and their boss—
and give them what they gave Grette. End them.
End them ALL.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0044
rows.name: ...Then it's over.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0045
rows.name:
It won't bring Adelbert and Grette back, but at least
those bastards paid for what they did.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0046
rows.name: That's justice. That's right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_JNK0110
rows.name: Nod

rows.label: qev015003_SEL0111
rows.name: Agree with Phina that justice was served.

rows.label: qev015003_JNK0120
rows.name: Disagree

rows.label: qev015003_SEL0121
rows.name: Tell Phina that revenge solves nothing.

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0047
rows.name:
Thank you. I'll...I'll head back to camp and tell Dirk
what happened.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0048
rows.name:
I want to repay you, as well, so please come by when
you can.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0049
rows.name: ...No? But isn't this what Grette kept me alive to do?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015003_MSG0050
rows.name:
I've got some thinking to do before I head back to
camp. ...Oh, but I want to repay you as well.
So please come by when you can.[ST:wait ]
